{"tid":1955853,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"瑞典有報章放左一張肺炎習近平既相","createTime":"2020-04-02T18:35:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T12:17:40.000Z","uid":222970,"like":604,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"19e4408b31ad01ebcb768399e5f985ac4f84fa3e","tid":1955853,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T18:35:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HeocTme.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHeocTme.jpg&h=22aad90c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9ca6XNU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9ca6XNU.jpg&h=317afb0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n瑞典《每日工業報》（左圖）3月30日在報紙第17版（右圖）全版抨擊中國的宣傳策略。（圖取自Dagens industri paper）<br />\n<br />\n撰寫文章的《每日工業報》記者約翰．尼蘭德（Johan Nylander）指出，要理解中國的宣傳，查看那些被審查的言論相當重要，但也應該要了解那些未經審查的內容，目前，批評中國領導人習近平散播新型冠狀病毒、操控疫情數據的聲浪正在被消除，與此同時，中國正隨意散佈荒謬的陰謀論─「病毒實際上並非來自中國」。<br />\n<br />\n有瑞典網友認為，中國共產黨的宣傳手法效法自納粹德國時期的國民教育與宣傳部部長約瑟夫．戈培爾（Joseph Goebbels），這號人物在當時被稱作「宣傳的天才」，以鐵腕捍衛希特勒政權和維持第三帝國的體制；也有網友認為，該報導是「一篇很好的文章，展現了共產黨專政的正確面孔。」"},{"pid":"32415d626db81297ea94e007e44e26513c805bce","tid":1955853,"uid":3149,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T18:49:56.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4a4b4488c8798d58e1a63c975fd1a51903f4fe3","tid":1955853,"uid":91511,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T18:52:33.000Z","msg":"近平病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b46fc2a7b760ccb7c1c38f260212c6e03a247ef4","tid":1955853,"uid":122920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-02T18:56:07.000Z","msg":"pushh"},{"pid":"ffe48d9e1207989b787ff715dc395f27ca2aea31","tid":1955853,"uid":296705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":